<tr><td><table BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=5 CELLPADDING=0 ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=100%>
<tr><td><font face="Comic Sans MS" size=2><font color=#800000><a name=4></a><b><br>WE OPEN NEW SITE!</b></font><font color=#006600 size=1> [ <a href=mailto:eq_trade@usa.net target=main><font color=#006600>ShadowMaster</font></a> at 17:10 CST ]</font></font></tr></td>
<tr><td><font face="Comic Sans MS" size=2>We open new site about Asheron's Call. New miltiplayer online RPG by Turbine/Microsoft. Chek it <a href=http://www.eqtrade.com/ac/> University of Asheron </a><br><br>Thanks !</font></td></tr>
